  <channel>
    <title>CKAN: Ticket #1404: Post-v1.5 UX improvements</title>
    <link>http://localhost/ticket/1404</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
Various UX improvements, bugs, and suggestions are collected here:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[general]: Empty tables have a '(none)' placeholder which is causing issues. Move it into a separate div - it doesn't need be a wide &amp;lt;td&amp;gt; object.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[dataset/edit]: Errors in form - would be nice to auto-open the appropriate resource box.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[search]: Declutter the sidebar. No yellow box.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[search]: Facets to go on the left, rather than the right. More logical flow.
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[dataset/edit]: No hint is given that the time format for a resource is in ISO, eg 2005-01-01T10:10:10
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
